## Slug Algorithm

The Slug algorithm for GPU-centered font rendering directly from glyph outlines
was created by Eric Lengyel (Terathon Software).

- Paper: "GPU-Centered Font Rendering Directly from Glyph Outlines"
  Journal of Computer Graphics Techniques (JCGT), Vol. 6, No. 2, pp. 31-47, 2017
  https://jcgt.org/published/0006/02/02/

- US Patent #10,373,352 was dedicated to the public domain via terminal disclaimer
  filed March 17, 2026.

- Reference implementation (HLSL shaders):
  https://github.com/EricLengyel/Slug

